{"tid":1630774,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［好重要］popo涉嫌縱火燒觀塘站 制造理由停鐵 嫁禍示威者 要求黨鐵公布cctvb紀錄","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:37:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T23:27:17.000Z","uid":48083,"like":28,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"16b0bd25928296bb938f9af690688193c9687f7e","tid":1630774,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:37:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rJXbXq8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrJXbXq8.png&h=8d0c664a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解咁重要？<br />\n<br />\n777搞到全港封站，一來少人示威，更重要係制造對其他市民極大不便，並將責任嫁禍示威者<br />\n<br />\n哩兩日搭巴士，好多街坊屌哂鬼，講緊個個要兩三小時番屋企<br />\n我敢講，&lsquo;導致全港封鐵&rsquo;既責任<br />\n如果繼續出現並入示威者數<br />\n係絕對足夠令一些淺黃/中立轉邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因此一定要講清楚好大程度係政府玩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8a4bd2cb39064b7c306d9df1f09179e7e4d826","tid":1630774,"uid":52928,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:39:46.000Z","msg":"任何人都可以做示威者<br />\n但無人可以扮警察<br />\n冷處理"},{"pid":"6956eb77adab9325da41019f15f370cdef83c039","tid":1630774,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:49:00.000Z","msg":"黨鐵<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">春袋</span></span>係<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">控制室</span></span><br />\n好多車站開唔到都係因為控制室維修唔到<br />\n因為所有訊號同指示都係由控制室傳達"},{"pid":"4ae3178403755ecb0ae3ddc0f77f4c53dde97a3f","tid":1630774,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6956eb77adab9325da41019f15f370cdef83c039","tid":163